cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.MM, cs.CL 

The paper deals with image classification and annotation using visual cues and metadata from social media. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves information retrieval and semantic embeddings, which are related to cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The use of social media metadata suggests a possible fit with cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The use of neural networks for image classification and annotation is related to cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves natural language processing and text analysis, which are related to cs.CL (Computation and Language).
